<Process Id="1058" Name="Preparing Business Cases" ReferenceNo="" Objective="To set out the process to be followed to prepare a business case to get a captial project considered by Council for inclusion in years 1, 2 or 3 of a Long Term Plan (LTP).|~||~|This includes multi-year projects beginning in years 1, 2 or 3.|~||~|Business cases should be prepared for capital projects expected to cost $500,000 or more.|~||~|Note that projects for inclusion in years 4 to 10 of the LTP will be taken from the approved AMP." IsTouchModeEnabled="false" IsTextModeOn="false" UseDynamicMapperImage="true" Background="" Owner="Promapp Promaster" OwnerId="1" Expert="Promapp Promaster" ExpertId="1" Group="Finance" GroupId="201" GroupUniqueId="eb358656-d641-4b38-8794-35ea5c6d57b7" State="Active" StateId="1" Version="2.0" PromappVersion="4.6.2.14" UniqueId="a6e5efce-6fc5-44bc-84de-30c12850b137" IsPolicyModeOn="false" IsVirtualVariation="false">
